CVE-2014-0230    (AV:N/AC:L/Au:N/C:N/I:N/A:C)       7.8
CVE-2014-7810    (AV:N/AC:L/Au:N/C:N/I:P/A:N)       5.0
===========================================================
             Information on CVSS is documented
            in HP Customer Notice: HPSN-2008-002

RESOLUTION

HPE has provided the following software updates to resolve these
vulnerabilities in HP-UX Tomcat 6.

Tomcat 6.0.45.01 for HP-UX Release B.11.31 (IPF and PA-RISC)

64 bit Depot: HP_UX_11.31_HPUXWS22ATW-B407-11-31-64.depot
32 bit Depot: HP_UX_11.31_HPUXWS22ATW-B407-11-31-32.depot

Note: The depot files can be found here: https://h20392.www2.hpe.com/portal/s
wdepot/displayProductInfo.do?productNumber=HPUXWSATW407

MANUAL ACTIONS: Yes - Update Download and install the software update

PRODUCT SPECIFIC INFORMATION

HP-UX Software Assistant: HP-UX Software Assistant is an enhanced application
that replaces HP-UX Security Patch Check. It analyzes all Security Bulletins
issued by HP and lists recommended actions that may apply to a specific HP-UX
system. It can also download patches and create a depot automatically. For
more information see: https://www.hp.com/go/swa

The following text is for use by the HP-UX Software Assistant.

AFFECTED VERSIONS

HP-UX B.11.31 IA/PA
===================
hpuxws22Tomcat.hpuxws22TOMCAT.TOMCAT
action: install C.6.0.45.01 or subsequent

END AFFECTED VERSIONS

